WEBVTT

00:16.015 --> 00:17.350
(typing)

00:18.518 --> 00:20.937
-(text whooshes)
-(clears throat)

00:23.648 --> 00:25.608
(clicks tongue)

00:25.692 --> 00:28.611
All right, y'all,
I'm finna head out.

00:28.695 --> 00:30.488
Wait, you're, uh,
you're leavin'?

00:30.572 --> 00:32.031
(phone dings)

00:32.115 --> 00:34.159
Yeah, I'm about
to leave right now.

00:40.790 --> 00:43.793
(eerie music playing)

00:43.877 --> 00:47.714
Is-is everything good?

00:47.797 --> 00:51.176
