found Mouse's body.

01:14.240 --> 01:16.493
(glass shatters)

01:17.285 --> 01:18.536
Faye:
Sorry.

01:41.935 --> 01:43.478
(tense music)

01:43.561 --> 01:45.814
Did you hear what I said?

01:45.897 --> 01:47.190
Ch-ch-ch...

01:47.273 --> 01:52.862
I thought you
told me that Laurie
killed Mouse, right?

01:52.946 --> 01:54.364
-Faye: Laurie?
-Wha--

01:55.865 --> 01:57.325
I never said that.

01:57.408 --> 01:59.202
What are you
talkin' about?

01:59.285 --> 02:01.037
Yeah, you know, Laurie,

02:01.120 --> 02:05.333
the drug dealer that
lives in the apartment
complex off Kemper.

02:05.416 --> 02:09.337
Yeah, you were
the one that told me
she killed Mouse.

02:09.420 --> 02:11.172
I never said that.

02:13.466 --> 02:16.761
-Yes, you did.
-Custer: What are
you talking about?

02:16.845 --> 02:18.888
-Are you high?
-Faye: You know that
Laurie and those

02:18.972 --> 02:20.348
fucking people,
they scare me.

02:20.431 --> 02:22.058
