to protect them?

02:22.141 --> 02:24.143
I'm not fuckin'
protecting anyone.

02:24.227 --> 02:25.562
What the fuck is this?

02:25.645 --> 02:28.106
-So, you're working for Laurie?
-Custer: Hey, no!

02:28.189 --> 02:30.191
So how about you
just shut the fuck up!

02:30.275 --> 02:35.280
