trying to cover up a murder
that she committed?

02:35.363 --> 02:37.907
-(nervous laughter)
-Fezco: All right, now.

02:37.991 --> 02:40.410
Think it's time
for you to get outta
here, big fella.

02:40.493 --> 02:44.163
Bro... we gotta figure out
what the fuck we're gonna say.

02:44.247 --> 02:46.958
