a fucking issue.
-Wait, Ash. Ash, Ash!

02:47.041 --> 02:48.126
No!

02:48.209 --> 02:49.919
(Custer wheezing)

02:53.006 --> 02:54.215
(grunting)

02:54.841 --> 02:56.217
(wheezing)

03:00.597 --> 03:02.724
(Custer grunting)

03:12.275 --> 03:14.110
