Do you ever think
about the future?

03:57.445 --> 04:00.073
-Fezco: (on phone)
Yeah, all the time.
-Really?

04:00.156 --> 04:01.950
Fezco: Yeah.

04:02.033 --> 04:03.409
Lexi: (on phone)
Like you have a plan?

04:03.493 --> 04:06.829
