see you as a farmer.

04:14.128 --> 04:15.505
Fezco:
Yeah, fuck it.

04:15.588 --> 04:19.634
Get some horses, cows,
pigs, chickens, goats.

04:19.717 --> 04:21.386
Have a little family.

04:23.346 --> 04:26.349
Like some "Little House
on the Prairie"-type shit.
You know?

04:26.432 --> 04:28.101
I don't know
if I know that show.

04:28.184 --> 04:31.145
Fezco:
You never heard of "Little
House on the Prairie"?

04:31.229 --> 04:33.022
Lexi: Okay, this might
sound kind of crazy but,

04:33.106 --> 04:35.608
my plan is to have,
like, three kids at 30.

04:35.692 --> 04:38.069
Like, each one
a year and a half apart.

04:38.152 --> 04:40.738
