I can focus on,

04:40.822 --> 04:43.908
you know, being a good mom
and raising my kids,
et cetera, et cetera.

04:43.992 --> 04:47.453
And then, drop the last one
off at college at 58.

04:47.537 --> 04:49.664
Which will give me,
like, 32 years

04:49.747 --> 04:52.166
to focus on me
and live my life

04:52.250 --> 04:54.377
