this shit all figured out, huh?

04:57.463 --> 05:00.216
Lexi:
Yeah. (laughs)
It's kind of crazy, right?

05:00.299 --> 05:02.510
I mean...

05:02.593 --> 05:05.346
they got, they got
three kids in that show.

05:06.973 --> 05:09.934
