thinkin' or feelin'?

05:45.428 --> 05:46.971
Lexi:
I don't know.
You can connect

05:47.055 --> 05:48.639
with people who have
similar interests.

05:48.723 --> 05:50.433
Fezco: Mmm.
I just feel like people

05:50.516 --> 05:52.602
be sharin' way
too much on there.

05:52.685 --> 05:54.353
-Online?
-Yeah.

05:54.437 --> 05:57.023
