Not you.

26:14.531 --> 26:15.824
Mm-mm. No.

26:15.907 --> 26:19.619
C'mon, now go wash
your fucking hands.

26:19.703 --> 26:21.246
I love you, brother.

26:25.166 --> 26:27.294
(tense music playing)

26:46.771 --> 26:48.815
