Yep.

30:25.782 --> 30:27.575
Got all the best
parts of him.

30:28.535 --> 30:30.411
Think I know
what part that is.

30:30.495 --> 30:32.622
(all laughing)

30:40.046 --> 30:42.674
You know what I think
we have in common?

30:47.178 --> 30:49.806
When we both get off
on hurting other people.

30:50.598 --> 30:52.058
What do ya think?

30:55.603 --> 30:58.481
-You wanna talk
about this upstairs?
-Nate: No.

