31:24.632 --> 31:25.883
Ya happy?

31:28.469 --> 31:29.846
I'm figuring it out.

31:29.929 --> 31:31.472
(can opens)

31:34.517 --> 31:35.685
Sorry.

31:36.728 --> 31:38.855
(friends chuckling)

