33:39.183 --> 33:40.935
I fucked up, Nate...

33:43.855 --> 33:45.356
but I love you.

33:46.983 --> 33:48.484
I love you.

33:49.485 --> 33:50.862
And I should've
protected you,

33:50.945 --> 33:53.573
I should've
kept you safe,
and I didn't.

33:54.240 --> 33:55.783
I didn't.

33:58.244 --> 34:00.663
And there's nothing
I regret more.

34:07.336 --> 34:09.464
I don't want your apology.

34:15.386 --> 34:17.513
I just want revenge.

34:18.598 --> 34:20.266
What does that mean?

34:31.736 --> 34:33.488
What is that?

34:39.786 --> 34:41.370
It's everything.

34:44.999 --> 34:46.417
Everything.

34:49.462 --> 34:51.589
(car pulls up)

34:53.257 --> 34:54.509
Nate...

34:55.593 --> 34:57.011
(car door opens)

34:57.929 --> 34:59.263
don't do this.

34:59.347 --> 35:00.348
(car door closes)

35:00.431 --> 35:01.766
Nate, look at me.

35:02.934 --> 35:04.894
Do not do this.

35:06.854 --> 35:07.897
Nate, don't do this.

35:07.980 --> 35:09.482
I'm, I'm,
I'm begging you.

35:09.565 --> 35:11.984
-Don't do this.
-You are...

35:12.068 --> 35:13.528
who you are.

35:16.239 --> 35:18.449
I don't think you're
ever gonna change.

35:36.968 --> 35:39.762
Chief Greenwood?
He's in here.

35:43.307 --> 35:45.309
Thanks, Nate.
Appreciate it.

36:01.200 --> 36:03.119
Cal, you're under arrest.

36:03.202 --> 36:05.663
Put your hands
behind your head.

36:05.746 --> 36:06.998
