37:25.451 --> 37:27.411
Ash, come outta there!

37:27.495 --> 37:28.746
Officer: Drop your knife!

37:28.829 --> 37:31.082
Move slowly!
There's a kid in here!

37:31.165 --> 37:32.458
Please, don't shoot!

37:32.541 --> 37:34.919
-Please, Ash, come out!
