37:53.646 --> 37:56.148
(screaming):
Ash!

37:56.232 --> 37:58.526
(rapid gunfire)

38:04.532 --> 38:06.492
(screaming):
Ash!

38:10.579 --> 38:12.123
(groans)

38:16.460 --> 38:17.545
Don't shoot!

38:17.628 --> 38:21.465
Ash, come on!
Get outta there!

38:22.508 --> 38:25.720
(tense music playing)

38:28.639 --> 38:33.227
