39:16.854 --> 39:18.022
Ash!

39:21.692 --> 39:23.194
Ash!

39:24.904 --> 39:27.448
Ash! Ash!

39:28.908 --> 39:30.159
Answer me!

39:30.242 --> 39:32.369
(glass crunching)

39:33.662 --> 39:36.540
(coughing)
Ash!

39:46.133 --> 39:47.384
Shh.

39:49.970 --> 39:52.932
(tense, percussive music)

