it was silent.

41:08.632 --> 41:12.845
My... my first
thought was...

41:12.928 --> 41:15.055
"This feels
like a movie."

41:17.391 --> 41:19.018
I know a lot of people
feel that way when

41:19.101 --> 41:21.270
traumatic things
happen to them.

41:24.231 --> 41:27.026
Uh, at least,
I, I hear that a lot.

41:28.319 --> 41:30.362
It didn't feel real.

41:34.700 --> 41:36.660
It felt like a movie.

41:38.621 --> 41:40.414
Uh, and this is it.
This is...

41:40.498 --> 41:43.792
This is the part where
the character never recovers.

41:47.838 --> 41:51.050
The part where...
life takes them down.

41:52.384 --> 41:53.844
This is the s--

41:56.055 --> 41:58.557
This is the scene
that scars her forever.

41:58.641 --> 42:00.768
(classical piano playing)

42:02.228 --> 42:03.771
(door opens)

42:06.607 --> 42:08.025
Suze: Lexi.

42:08.108 --> 42:10.819
-Get dressed. It's your dad.
-Lexi: What?

42:15.908 --> 42:17.993
♪ ♪

42:23.749 --> 42:26.168
(music intensifies)

42:31.257 --> 42:33.342
