1:00:08.563 --> 1:00:12.108
♪ You know I'm trying ♪

1:00:13.443 --> 1:00:15.069
♪ Hey, Lord ♪

1:00:15.153 --> 1:00:18.781
♪ You know I'm trying ♪

1:00:20.408 --> 1:00:23.703
♪ It's all I got ♪

1:00:23.786 --> 1:00:27.248
♪ Is this enough ♪

1:00:27.332 --> 1:00:32.170
♪ Hey Lord,
I wanna stay ♪

1:00:33.755 --> 1:00:35.381
♪ Hey, Lord ♪

1:00:35.465 --> 1:00:39.552
♪ You know I'm fighting ♪

1:00:40.595 --> 1:00:42.305
♪ Hey, Lord ♪

1:00:42.388 --> 1:00:47.226
♪ You know I'll fight it ♪

1:00:47.310 --> 1:00:54.442
♪ I don't know when
or how today ♪

1:00:54.525 --> 1:00:59.155
♪ Hey, Lord,
I'm on my way ♪

